<p>Step back in time to the 1920s and 30s and enjoy an evening of dinner and dancing at the Cumberland Heritage Village Museum. Treat yourself to a delicious roast supper and live music by local musicians. Put on your dancing shoes and hit the dance floor as our guest caller takes you through the steps for an authentic barn dance experience. Immerse yourself in the ambiance of the era-appropriate museum grounds for a truly unique evening out with friends and family.</p>
